	<tr>
		<td valign=middle align=left width=22><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=1 width=20 border=0></td>
		<td valign=middle align=right class="header">Creating A Task</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2"><hr size="1"></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click New Task</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Enter these compulsory fields; date, time and description</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Reminders will be send to you via memo</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">4.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click here to specify if you allow the assignee to re-assign this task to another person</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">5.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Who do you want to assign this task to… Click Select</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">6.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Select the resource(s) you need for this meeting. Use the '>>' button to bring them into the Selected box.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">7.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">If set to Private, the details of the task cannot be seen by other users</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">8.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Finally, click Submit. The new task will check for availability of the resource(s)</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">9.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">If there is a conflict of resource use, you will be prompted to continue to save or cancel.</td>
	</tr>
</table>
